      <title>GPS 導航製造商 Trimble 預測季度業績不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/gps-navigation-maker-trimble-forecasts-downbeat-quarterly-results-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析和軟體公司 Trimble 週五預測第二季業績低於華爾街預期，受到其產品和服務需求低迷的影響，導致其股價下跌約 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/gps-navigation-maker-trimble-forecasts-downbeat-quarterly-results-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 15:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
