      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/synopsys-nears-2-billion-plus-software-unit-sale-buyout-firms-sources-say-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 17:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
